attentionNote.value: For your convenience, certain input fields are pre-filled with data extracted from your tax return for last year.  Please check the data and amend them as appropriate.  It is your responsibility to ensure all data input are correct and that there is no omission.

For your convenience, certain input fields are pre-filled with data extracted from IRD records as at the TAX RETURN ISSUE DATE.  Please check the data and amend them as appropriate.  It is your responsibility to ensure all data input are correct and that there is no omission.

For your convenience, the employment particulars are pre-filled with data extracted from IRD records as at 10/05/2022.  The availability of your current year income amount details is dependent on when the Employer's Returns are filed.  Please check the data and amend them as appropriate.  It is your responsibility to ensure all data input are correct and that there is no omission.  



If you have amended any of the pre-filled income amounts, please consider leave your reason in the text box of "Supplementary Information on Tax Return" by clicking the "Supplement" button at the bottom of the screen.

adhocMessage1.value: If your computer remains inactive for a period of time after login, the system will log out itself automatically to prevent any unauthorised access.
